{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":{"eng-name":"The Chapters on Marriage","ara-name":"كتاب النكاح"}},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1984,"arabicnumber":1984,"text":"حدثنا ابو بكر بن ابي شيبة، حدثنا وكيع، عن هشام بن عروة، عن ابيه، عن عايشة، قالت ما ضرب رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم خادما له ولا امراة ولا ضرب بيده شييا","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":140},"chapter":{"id":51,"ara-name":"باب ضَرْبِ النِّسَاءِ","eng-name":"Hitting women","isFirstHadith":false}}]}